items.name: Plantronics M70 Bluetooth Headset
items.shortDescription: The Plantronics M70 Bluetooth Headset is so lightweight and comfortable that you may forget you're wearing it. During setup, you simply follow the voice prompts to select English, Spanish or French for the audible status alerts on talk time, battery level, connection and more. You can also control music tracks and volume without touching your smartphone. If you forget the Bluetooth headset for smartphone in the car or at the office, the M70 knows to enter its DeepSleep hibernation mode to conserve the battery. Using it is so easy that you can finally free your cheek from your smartphone. It reduces wind and noise for a clear and crisp quality call and it makes for a comfortable fit with the three optional ear tips to choose from. <br>
items.longDescription: The Plantronics M70 Bluetooth Headset allows you to do more with your voice and answer calls without even pressing a button and you can manage emails and much more. It stays charged up, so it's always ready when you want to hear some music or just make a call.<br> <br><b>Plantronics M70 Bluetooth Headset:</b><ul><li>Plantronics Blutetooth headset features language options for status alerts</li><li>Hear music, videos and more</li><li>Power-saving mode</li><li>Reduces noise, wind and echo from calls</li><li>DeepSleep hibernation mode</li><li>Free Plantronics Find MyHeadset app</li><li>Talk Time: up to 11 h</li><li>Standby Time: up to 16 days</li></ul>

items.name: Motorola H730 Bluetooth Headset
items.shortDescription: <p>The Motorola H730 Headset's classic flip boom design lets you answer calls with a simple flip and ensures comfort. Powered by lithium ion battery, the Motorola Bluetooth Headset offers up to 12 hours talk time and can be easily charged using its inbuilt micro USB connector port. You can easily configure this micro USB Bluetooth lightweight headset with two phones and enjoy the luxury of attending calls from both of them. The Motorola Bluetooth Headset promptly tells you when you to connect, which phone is ringing and even about the battery level. The tow inbuilt dual-mics cancel noise and help you make conversations more clearly. This Motorola H730 Headset has a very convenient design that makes it easy to use and doesn't put any strain on your ears even after prolonged hours of usage. The cushioned hinges allow for behind ear wearing style.</p>
items.longDescription: <br><strong>Motorola H730 Bluetooth Headset:</strong><ul class="noindent"><li>Micro USB connector port</li><li>Connect simultaneously to two mobile phones</li><li>EasyPair technology</li><li>Dual-mics cancel noise</li><li>12 hours of talk time</li><li>Behind ear wearing style</li><li>Lightweight and cushioned</li></ul>

items.name: Plantronics Voyager Legend Bluetooth Model 87300-60
items.shortDescription: Enjoy an enhanced hands-free experience with this handy Plantronics Voyager Legend Bluetooth headset. It is made of sturdy and durable materials designed for long-lasting use. This Voyager Bluetooth headset features triple-microphones that cancel noise and wind and voice commands for added convenience. It uses Smart Sensor technology that is designed to understand how and when you want to talk, and it provides up to seven hours of talk time and 11 days of standby time.
items.longDescription: <br><b>Plantronics Voyager Legend Bluetooth Headset:</b><ul><li>Smart Sensor technology</li><li>Noise-cancelling</li><li>Wind-cancelling</li><li>Moisture protection</li><li>Multi-point protection</li><li>Bluetooth v3.0 technology</li><li>Rechargeable lithium-ion polymer battery</li><li>Charge time: 90 min</li><li>Talk time: up to 7 hours</li><li>Plantronics Legend bluetooth headset has standby time of up to 11 days</li></ul>

items.name: Plantronics M165 Marque 2 Bluetooth Headset, Black
items.shortDescription: Receive calls easily and safely as you drive with this handy Plantronics M165 Marque 2 Bluetooth Headset. It features a deep sleep power saving mode that conserves its charge when it isn't in use so it can be ready when you need it. This black Bluetooth headset also has dual mic noise reduction so your calls can be clear and free of distracting background noise. It also allows you to manage calls hands-free without pressing any buttons so you can keep your focus on the road. This Plantronics Marque 2 Bluetooth headset will even allow you to conveniently stream your favorite music or driving directions from your smartphone or tablet. Its many useful features mean that you will want to use it for traveling and commuting as well as when you are relaxing at home. Getting the most from your phone and talking on the go can be simple with the Plantronics M165 Marque 2 Bluetooth Headset.
items.longDescription: <b><br>Plantronics M165 Marque 2 Bluetooth Headset, Black:</b><br><ul><li>DeepSleep power-saving mode</li><li>Plantronics Marque 2 Bluetooth headset with dual-mic noise reduction</li><li>Manage calls without pressing a button</li><li>Stream music, radio, videos or driving directions from your smartphone or tablet</li><li>Color: black</li><li>This Plantronics Marque 2 Bluetooth headset is ideal for hands-free calling</li></ul>

items.name: Jabra Bluetooth Headset
items.shortDescription: <p>Own a listening device that is easy to use with other electronics with the Jabra Bluetooth Headset. It has an easy-to-use button and an auto pairing feature when connected to two devices simultaneously. The Bluetooth cellphone headset offers clear sound as well as eight hours of continuous talk time and days of standby time. Have dependable conversations without interference or muffled sound with this device.</p>
items.longDescription: <b>Jabra Bluetooth Headset:</b><ul><li>A wireless Bluetooth headset that can be paired</li><li>Easy-to-use button and auto pairing when paired to 2 devices simultaneously</li><li>Wireless Bluetooth headset offers clear sound</li><li>8 hours of talk time and 10 days of standby time</li></ul>

items.name: Plantronics Voyager PRO HD
items.shortDescription: The Plantronics Voyager PRO HD Headset redefines hands-free convenience. This headset uses Smart Sensor technology that automatically answers your phone or transfers calls back and forth between your phone and headset. With this Plantronics Voyager Pro Bluetooth Headset, you can enjoy HD audio streaming and clear calls, and it will also pause the music when you have an incoming call. This device integrates with iPhone and Android smartphones, and you can see the headset's battery meter displayed on the phone's screen. The Plantronics hands-free headset also gives you voice alerts for talk time, volume, connection and more. With its comfortable ergonomic design, you can easily wear this Plantronics Voyager PRO HD Headset all day long.
items.longDescription: <b>Plantronics Voyager PRO HD:</b><br><ul><li>Smart Sensor technology knows whether to send calls to your mobile phone or your headset</li><li>Plantronics Voyager Pro Bluetooth hands-free headset eliminates accidental dialing by locking call button when headset is not worn</li><li>Streams music, podcasts and more</li><li>Pauses streaming audio for calls or when the Plantronics headset is taken off</li><li>Triple tapping the call button dials Vocalyst voice and text service</li><li>Plantronics MyHeadset app gives you tips, tricks and tools for Android-based phones</li><li>On-screen battery meter for iPhone and Android 3.0 or higher smartphones</li><li>Experience brilliant, HD streaming audio plus natural, clear calls</li><li>Voice alerts announce talk time, volume, connection and more</li><li>Plantronics headset with ergonomic all-day fit</li></ul>

items.name: Plantronics M55 Bluetooth Headset
items.shortDescription: The Plantronics M55 Bluetooth Headset allows you to do more with your voice with hands-free management. Answer and receive calls, stream music and media, listen to GPS directions and more over a wireless connection. It is compatible with most Bluetooth-enabled devices and has multi-point technology, which allows you to pair and maintain a connection between two phones simultaneously. It's voice-activated capabilities allow you to respond to calls by simply saying "answer" or "ignore." To ensure clear audio transmission, this Plantronics Bluetooth headset enhances call clarity on wideband-enabled smartphones and networks by reducing noise, wind and echo. The thin, rectangular design features an earbud covered by a clear silicone sheath with a looped stabilizer for a comfortable and secure fit.
items.longDescription: This smartphone Bluetooth headset includes a rechargeable lithium-ion polymer battery that delivers up to 11 hours of talk time, 16 days of standby time, fully charges in two hours and offers micro-USB charging.<br> <b>Plantronics M55 Bluetooth Headset:</b><ul><li>Take calls without pressing a button, just say "answer"</li><li>DeepSleep mode extends battery readiness for up to five months</li><li>Hear music, videos, driving directions and more from your smartphone</li><li>Voice alerts whisper talk time, battery level and more</li><li>Enhances clarity on wideband-enabled smartphones</li><li>Reduces noise, wind and echo from calls</li><li>Smartphone Bluetooth headset fits comfortably in either ear</li></ul>

items.name: Jabra TALK Bluetooth Headset
items.shortDescription: Stay in touch all the time and hear every conversation clearly with the easy-to-use Jabra TALK Bluetooth Headset. Every time you make a call, you'll hear it in HD sound quality for the ultimate in crisp, clear sound without confusion or disruptions. That means you can stay focused on the call and keep talking while you multitask. With the Jabra TALK Headset, you can stream multi-media, and it also features an automatic volume level. This headset can be used with two Bluetooth devices at the same time, and it also has a Voice Announcement function. The versatile device also has an On/Off slider so you can easily control it while you are wearing it.
items.longDescription: <b>Jabra TALK Bluetooth Headset:</b><br><ul><li>HD Voice technology</li><li>Stream multi-media</li><li>Voice Announcements</li><li>Multi-use connects 2 Bluetooth devices simultaneously</li><li>Automatic Volume adjustment</li><li>Jabra Bluetooth headset with On/Off slider control</li><li>Talk Time: up to 6 h</li><li>Standby Time: up to 8 days</li></ul>

items.name: Wireless Sport Stereo Headset Bluetooth Earphone headphone for Samsung LG iPhone -Black
items.longDescription: Enjoying your favorite tunes on the fly with this bluetooth stereo headset couldn't be easier. There's no need to plug your headphones into your smartphone or MP3 player which eliminates a lot of clutter. These bluetooth headphones pair effortlessly with your device and provide maximum comfort. You can also accept calls with this stereo headset which provides another level of convenience. The battery takes up to 2.5 hours to charge and when full, it can provide up to 6 hours of play time, up to 10 hours of talk time or over 10 days of standby time.
